---
title: Sesame Hoisin Chicken Legs with Garlic Scallion Rice & Roasted Broccoli
description: When it comes to chicken, we’re always looking for two things: golden, crackly skin and juicy, flavorful meat. Oh, you too? Enter: these game-changing roasted chicken legs. They’re all that and then some, the “some” being a dynamic hoisin-ginger-lime glaze that really takes ’em above and beyond. On the side, there’s garlic scallion rice and sesame-roasted broccoli. What are you waiting for?!
